Title: Validate if host label rules use predefined conditions with host labels
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1651489003
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b9

Werk 13372 introduced the possibility to use host label conditions in service
label rulesets but broke the validation, that host label rules can not use
predefined conditions with host label conditions.
